</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_65496984"><p>The <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Index_Librorum_Prohibitorum" title="wikipedia.org">Index Librorum Prohibitorum</a> [wikipedia.org] was a list of books deemed heretical. The idea was to stop people from reading things that might give people ideas that the Church did not like. Taking down these web sites is much the same thing: stop people getting ideas that those funding Trump do not like.</p></div>
	</div>

